data.description: Welcome to the country life! NO HOA, NO CITY TAXES, NO RESTRICTIONS! Enjoy the peaceful country on almost 1 acre. This beautiful home is surrounded by mature trees and has a covered front porch where you can watch sunsets. The living room has an open concept, luxury vinyl plank flooring, natural light, and plenty of space for entertaining. Kitchen includes: lots of cabinet space for storage, eat-in bar top, and opens to the dining area. This versatile property offers a feed-tack room, storage workshop with electricity, storm shelter, shed for additional storage, and is fully fenced. Horses and animals are welcome
